extensions.description: The $CYAI Token is the heartbeat of the CyreneAI ecosystem, powering a decentralized AI economy. It enables seamless AI agent deployment, staking for decentralized compute, and transactions in the marketplace for AI-driven services and models. Token holders gain governance rights, shaping protocol upgrades and earning ecosystem rewards. Enterprises leverage the token for secure, scalable AI automation, driving the Agentic Future with autonomy and innovation.
The largest countries in the world are battling over this.
The pigeon biggest opp of the lion
